703554f-a.text:
(1)
Church Ave., north side, east from Utica Ave. It the background, is a view of the JJohn Schenck House. The new building at the left, is
on the corner of 5cnd Street.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
Another view of the Schenck house, about two years later. The
new building is on the corner of 53rd Street.
September 1927.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
703554f-a.folder: Church Avenue & Utica Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
